Card data attribution
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Magic: The Gathering card data is sourced from Scryfall
(https://scryfall.com/docs/api) bulk data, used under Scryfall's terms.
This project is not produced by, endorsed by, supported by, or affiliated
with Scryfall.

This project bundles NO card data. The Scryfall oracle-cards bulk dataset
(~30k cards) is downloaded locally on first run; it is not redistributed as
part of this repository or any release artifact.

